{"tid":1667870,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Google 將修復 iPhone 免費上傳全尺寸照片到 Photos 的「臭蟲」","createTime":"2019-10-21T16:35:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-22T12:23:15.000Z","uid":22675,"like":5,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"2708e4c7b0bf3204b36e573e52aa4ff47477df86","tid":1667870,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T16:35:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?resize=2000%2C2000%2Cshrink&amp;image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2019-10%2F928ec2b0-f355-11e9-bfdf-fbd6d07b09fb&amp;client=a1acac3e1b3290917d92&amp;signature=62fed46515a4688f985c2834ee101c419aed8b87\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fo.aolcdn.com%2Fimages%2Fdims%3Fresize%3D2000%252C2000%252Cshrink%26image_uri%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fs.yimg.com%252Fos%252Fcreatr-uploaded-images%252F2019-10%252F928ec2b0-f355-11e9-bfdf-fbd6d07b09fb%26client%3Da1acac3e1b3290917d92%26signature%3D62fed46515a4688f985c2834ee101c419aed8b87&h=c75f5d36&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nGoogle 表明了將修復一個讓 iPhone 用戶享有將「全尺寸」照片上傳到 Photos，卻不會計算 Google Drive 空間使用的「臭蟲」。其實這樣說對 iPhone 並不太公平，因為問題的根源在於 iPhone 所使用的檔案格式 HEIC &mdash;&mdash; 這個 iPhone 自 2017 年開始使用的新格式和 JPG 相比有著更高的資訊密度，也就是說就算是 iPhone 的原生畫質，檔案也比 Google 的「高畫質」來得小，再加上 iPhone 的照片是 12MP 的解析度，也沒有超過 Google 高畫質的 16MP。如果 Google 今天硬要將它轉換成「高畫質」的 JPG 的話，除了要花費額外的運算資源之外，轉換出來的檔案還會比原來的 HEIC 更大，佔去更多 Google 的儲存空間，所以大概是因為這樣，Google 才沒有做處理的。<br />\n<br />\n然而，在連「親兒子」Pixel 4 都沒有免費全尺寸相片儲存的現在，反而是 iPhone 用戶（和 Samsung 用戶，如果你的照片畫質少於 16MP，且開啟 HEIC 模式的話）能無限存放全尺寸照片，對 Google 來說大概觀感終究是不太好。因此 Google 宣佈了將修復這個「臭蟲」，只是究竟要如何做，卻是個謎。如果只是為了和 Android 裝置齊平，而硬是將 HEIC 轉成較低畫質的 JPG 的話，對 Google 來說那是真正的吃力不討好；而如果讓 HEIC 相片也計算進儲存空間的話，iPhone 用戶就沒有了「免費」的選項了。"},{"pid":"5158c5f8d5b0724f0c7d1c818e6446037eed382d","tid":1667870,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T16:40:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://chinese.engadget.com/2019/10/21/google-to-fix-bug-that-lets-iphones-store-full-quality-photos/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchinese.engadget.com%2F2019%2F10%2F21%2Fgoogle-to-fix-bug-that-lets-iphones-store-full-quality-photos%2F&d=bp2T%2F%2B5c5q8hcpZmRI3qNpMONXnVHdpXbsFGehQCOpI%3D&h=05b212d4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://chinese.engadget.com/2019/10/21/google-to-fix-bug-that-lets-iphones-store-full-quality-photos/</a>"},{"pid":"2cbef61d237819f57d19ece1fd32587f52574915","tid":1667870,"uid":3331,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T20:31:41.000Z","msg":"魚蛋到極致<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05745c569c6142b6475abed2f3b03164dcc62c06","tid":1667870,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T05:12:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c65b2a2c8851e06b15facac1b254baae4f8e9c85","tid":1667870,"uid":89514,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T05:25:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a355fb006e16a01c9e9db23a43c40824c1d1a889","tid":1667870,"uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c65b2a2c8851e06b15facac1b254baae4f8e9c85","tid":1667870,"uid":89514,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T05:25:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T05:32:34.000Z","msg":"google仆街奶共唔係今時今日嘅事，同apple比，google只係有破壞無建設嘅公司"},{"pid":"f614b518aec7aaf6ede4a6ec8711017c64b91f52","tid":1667870,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T10:23:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c049e78299bc7fcf9891cf23dd36ce2d7bf30813","tid":1667870,"uid":275238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T10:25:35.000Z","msg":"攬抄<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c6f39dad41928579ec8010e333614a021213e89","t